                    <span>Keith Brown's book is a refreshing change from the 'stick in something about security in a side-bar' approach taken by so many authors. Finally a book which explains lucidly what amounts to a very complex topic; and does so in an understandable and enjoyable fashion. If there were 6 stars on the rating scale then it would get a 6...</span>
                  
